{
  "stem": "5810.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we'll contact the-- the same people on the underground, who I'm sure they must have had contact on a weekly or a monthly basis, whenever it was necessary for them to get paid.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one of the underground persons came down and talked to my mother and I, and said-- and explained that they probably could handle that-- if it was OK with the Barniche for me to adopt their names, and to be enrolled in a Catholic school, and hide my Jewish identity in every way.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that would mean, of course, I was then a very dark-haired boy-- a dark-haired boy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I believe I must have looked somewhat Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I also had some mannerism, because, after all, in my family we spoke Yiddish, and I suppose the accent came through.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And certain mannerism and certain things that I needed to lose and forget.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I do remember for one month straight on a daily basis, someone from the underground coming down to the cellar and teaching me the proper way, or the other way of not speaking French with this Jewish mannerism and accent.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They lightened my hair.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was decided then to enroll me in this Catholic school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is how I finally got out of the cellar-- where I believe I was there for six, seven months-- and go daily to a Catholic school.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I mean really Catholic, because daily I had to go to mass before going to class.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- I had a birth certificates-- a birth certificate naming me as Andre Barniche, the son of Jeanne and Emile Barniche.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I do believe, however, that the school administration, for so many things that happened while I was in school, must have known.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were priests.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
